Title: Python in VS Code Improves Jedi Language Server Support -- Visual Studio Magazine
Description: Visual Studio Code developers who subscribe to Insiders builds of Microsoft's Python extension now have access to improved support for the Jedi language server, which provides specific 'smarts' for the language.
